## Main results

- `KaehlerDifferential`: The module of kaehler differentials. For an `R`-algebra `S`, we provide
  the notation `Œ©[S‚ÅÑR]` for `KaehlerDifferential R S`.
  Note that the slash is `\textfractionsolidus`.
