  `A`-linear map `Œ©[A‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí Œ©[B‚ÅÑS]`.
- `KaehlerDifferential.map_surjective`:
  The sequence `Œ©[B‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí Œ©[B‚ÅÑA] ‚Üí 0` is exact.
- `KaehlerDifferential.exact_mapBaseChange_map`:
  The sequence `B ‚äó[A] Œ©[A‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí Œ©[B‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí Œ©[B‚ÅÑA]` is exact.
- `KaehlerDifferential.exact_kerCotangentToTensor_mapBaseChange`:
  If `A ‚Üí B` is surjective with kernel `I`, then
  the sequence `I/I¬≤ ‚Üí B ‚äó[A] Œ©[A‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí Œ©[B‚ÅÑR]` is exact.
- `KaehlerDifferential.mapBaseChange_surjective`:
  If `A ‚Üí B` is surjective, then the sequence `B ‚äó[A] Œ©[A‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí Œ©[B‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí 0` is exact.

